Class OperationLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.s1.cluster.dds.OperationLog

  • public class OperationLog
extends java.lang.Object
    Node local operation log. You should provide custom implementation - you should override this class and put its name to 'cluster.operationLogClass' options. Do not use this class in production - its log is in-memory.

 DEBUG - add,markDone
